By Andile Mngxitama “We supported the DA and the only fair thing the DA can do is support us” – Julius Malema How can the leader of the Red Berets speak so normally about supporting the Democratic Alliance (DA), a racist anti black party of land thieves and white monopoly capital (WMC)? Can those who support Juju explain this? What we know it that only a ideology-less opportunistic politician would do such a thing. To us this is deeply disturbing. It is the legitimation of racism by people who express fake anger at the Springboks. Think about it – working with the DA, but critising the Springboks? Ja nee… Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization. No related posts.